                    </h4>
                    <div className="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto">
                        <table className="w-full text-xs md:text-sm text-right min-w-[500px]">
                            <thead className="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700/50 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 uppercase font-bold border-b dark:border-gray-700">
                                <tr>
                                    <th className="px-4 py-4 w-12 text-center">#</th>
                                    <th className="px-4 py-4">وصف المهمة المنجزة</th>
